{"name":"Victoria Corvius","size":"medium","type":"humanoid","tag":"Seremeth, Helm, Heptagram","alignment":"Lawful Good","hitDice":"8","armorName":"plate","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":3,"otherArmorDesc":"10","speed":"30","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"0","flySpeed":"30","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"22 (5d8)","speedDesc":"30 ft.","strPoints":"20","dexPoints":"8","conPoints":"12","intPoints":"8","wisPoints":"12","chaPoints":"18","blindsight":"0","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"6","customCr":"1 (200 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The monster can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The monster regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the monster can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the monster can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The monster can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the monster's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the monster's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the monster dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Divine Smite","desc":"When [MON] makes a weapon attack, it may expend a spell slot to deal an extra [1d8] radiant damage per spell level."},{"name":"Spellcasting","desc":"[MON]'s spellcasting ability is Charisma (spell save DC [CHA SAVE], [CHA ATK] to hit). [MON] has the following spells prepared:\n\n> 1st level (4 slots): _Searing Smite, Thunderous Smite, Wrathful Smite_\n> 2nd level (2 slots): _Magic Weapon, Branding Smite_"}],"actions":[{"name":"Multiattack","desc":"The [MON] makes two weapon attacks."},{"name":"Ragnarok","desc":"[MON] swings her holy sword as it unleashes a fiery, divine fury. [STR ATK] to hit one target. _Hit:_ [STR 1D10] radiant damage. Your divine smite affects all creatures within a 15ft cone."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[{"name":"Castle of Stone","desc":"[MON] channels the divine powers of the sword to halve any incoming damage taken."},{"name":"Divine Retribution","desc":"When a creature within 60ft. attacks [MON], it may invoke the powers of Helm to deal [2d10] radiant damage to the creature (halved if they succeed a **DC [CHA SAVE]** Dex Save)."}],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[{"name":"str","order":0},{"name":"cha","order":5}],"skills":[{"name":"athletics","stat":"str"},{"name":"religion","stat":"int"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"Victoria","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":true,"separationPoint":1,"damage":[]}